1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:28,910
[The Fearless Season 1]

3
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:31,789
[Episode 39]

4
00:01:33,240 --> 00:01:34,990
If they have to sacrifice me to make the connection,

5
00:01:34,990 --> 00:01:36,080
then so be it.

6
00:01:37,170 --> 00:01:39,500
I'm doing better than other kids, anyway.

7
00:01:44,190 --> 00:01:47,030
If I had no moral obligation whatsoever,

8
00:01:47,670 --> 00:01:49,110
I would be another Wen Li,

9
00:01:50,310 --> 00:01:51,840
desperately seizing anything good for me

10
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,390
within my reach.

11
00:01:53,729 --> 00:01:54,910
Then, turn to the next target

12
00:01:54,910 --> 00:01:56,470
without hesitation.

13
00:01:56,550 --> 00:01:57,460
Not me.

14
00:01:58,110 --> 00:01:59,009
I can't do that.

15
00:01:59,990 --> 00:02:01,710
What I can do is

16
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:04,410
not go back to the previous environment,

17
00:02:05,410 --> 00:02:07,190
live independently,

18
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:10,440
and do whatever I can to support them.

19
00:02:12,830 --> 00:02:13,810
Does your sacrifice

20
00:02:13,810 --> 00:02:15,740
also include your love?

21
00:02:19,390 --> 00:02:20,920
Forget about love.

22
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:24,270
It's simply a practical necessity.

23
00:02:28,070 --> 00:02:29,390
Anyway, for me right now,

24
00:02:29,390 --> 00:02:31,590
Zhang Quanquan should be my top choice.

25
00:02:36,950 --> 00:02:38,230
I think

26
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:43,800
if you even choose love so rationally,

27
00:02:44,870 --> 00:02:46,310
it's too...

28
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:50,410
Anyway, you don't have to do that.

29
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,920
You have already left there,

30
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:57,450
and now you're getting better and better.

31
00:02:58,880 --> 00:03:01,070
You deserve someone better.

32
00:03:01,510 --> 00:03:02,490
I have no choice.

33
00:03:02,990 --> 00:03:06,120
Human beings are the summation of all social relations.

34
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:08,120
Are you done already?

35
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,400
It doesn't need to take long.

36
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:17,480
Come on.

37
00:03:17,900 --> 00:03:19,579
I've made your bed for you.

38
00:03:28,079 --> 00:03:28,840
Good night.

39
00:03:45,550 --> 00:03:46,270
Yingzi.

40
00:03:48,790 --> 00:03:50,520
Chen Shuo fell in love with you.

41
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,200
Are you aware of that?

42
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:55,380
Are you kidding me?

43
00:03:56,110 --> 00:03:57,590
The bystander knows.

44
00:03:58,110 --> 00:03:59,420
I saw it clearly.

45
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,920
So, is he a sadist?

46
00:04:06,430 --> 00:04:08,990
He loves me and sent me to jail.

47
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:13,270
I don't think he has anything to do with that matter.

48
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:15,820
Even if there is, it's just a coincidence.

49
00:04:16,829 --> 00:04:18,170
Otherwise, he wouldn't have

50
00:04:18,170 --> 00:04:19,980
given us the CCTV footage.

51
00:04:22,910 --> 00:04:23,840
He's a nice guy.

52
00:04:24,990 --> 00:04:25,850
Don't miss him.

53
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:29,460
No way.

54
00:04:49,590 --> 00:04:52,180
[Na Young-ja]

55
00:04:54,010 --> 00:04:54,870
Righteous Luo.

56
00:04:55,080 --> 00:04:56,840
So, you still remember me.

57
00:04:57,470 --> 00:04:58,180
Chen Shuo.

58
00:05:02,440 --> 00:05:03,280
What's wrong?

59
00:05:03,590 --> 00:05:05,050
Are you still in Qingyang?

60
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:07,910
How is it going over there?

61
00:05:09,030 --> 00:05:10,820
Everything is under control.

62
00:05:12,910 --> 00:05:14,380
You must keep an eye on her.

63
00:05:16,350 --> 00:05:18,110
Don't let her escape so easily.

64
00:05:20,410 --> 00:05:21,720
I have a feeling.

65
00:05:22,350 --> 00:05:23,040
I think

66
00:05:23,150 --> 00:05:25,150
that if we can't catch her this time,

67
00:05:26,070 --> 00:05:27,700
we may never find her again.

68
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,840
What's going on?

69
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:32,350
Did something happen?

70
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:34,480
Why does your voice sound like this?

71
00:05:35,350 --> 00:05:36,040
Nothing.

72
00:05:36,650 --> 00:05:38,670
We came to her hometown.

73
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:41,440
We listened to her childhood stories.

74
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:44,230
She must have lived a very miserable life when she was young,

75
00:05:44,230 --> 00:05:46,090
and you feel sorry for her, right?

76
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:48,840
Chen Shuo.

77
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:51,670
Listen.

78
00:05:51,670 --> 00:05:54,130
You can definitely make a fortune this time.

79
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:57,580
If possible,

80
00:05:57,580 --> 00:05:59,930
I hope you can put down your work,

81
00:06:00,140 --> 00:06:01,540
keep an eye on her in Shanghai,

82
00:06:01,540 --> 00:06:03,140
and wait for me to come there.

83
00:06:03,170 --> 00:06:04,480
Then we can discuss

84
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:05,600
what to do next.

85
00:06:06,830 --> 00:06:07,750
This time,

86
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:09,350
I must stop her.

87
00:06:09,710 --> 00:06:10,470
Fine.

88
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:11,550
For you,

89
00:06:11,590 --> 00:06:14,030
I'm willing to give up all the opportunities to make big money.

90
00:06:14,030 --> 00:06:15,910
I do.

91
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:17,790
Come on.

92
00:06:18,270 --> 00:06:19,710
Thank you. Bye.

93
00:06:25,190 --> 00:06:25,790
Sir,

94
00:06:25,910 --> 00:06:26,850
I'm not going to Pudong Airport.

95
00:06:26,850 --> 00:06:31,050
Turn around at the next traffic light intersection and go back to the hotel.

96
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:47,760
Do you believe that some people are born with criminal personalities?

97
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:50,270
But I don't think Wen Li is.

98
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:53,600
Every person who's worked their way up from the bottom

99
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,070
goes through the same struggles as her,

100
00:06:55,070 --> 00:06:57,900
and some of them have even endured more hardships than her.

101
00:06:57,900 --> 00:06:59,909
But why did she become so vicious?

102
00:07:03,470 --> 00:07:04,180
I think

103
00:07:05,710 --> 00:07:07,510
maybe it's because other people

104
00:07:08,150 --> 00:07:10,030
can feel more or less love

105
00:07:10,030 --> 00:07:12,550
from society or from others,

106
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:15,010
while she never feels loved by others

107
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:16,410
except for her mother.

108
00:07:16,590 --> 00:07:17,110
No.

109
00:07:17,110 --> 00:07:18,530
You helped her.

110
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,160
And those men who were her prey

111
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:23,240
loved her and gave her their love.

112
00:07:23,570 --> 00:07:24,960
Could it be that she lost her empathy

113
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,620
when she met me and my husband?

114
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:28,840
Anyway, I feel sorry for her now.

115
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:32,230
How pitiful and horrible it is for a person

116
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:34,500
to lose the ability to feel love.

117
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,810
You still know that?

118
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,140
What?

119
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:43,110
It's pitiful to lose the ability to feel love.

120
00:07:49,510 --> 00:07:52,500
A money-grubber who wants nothing but money.

121
00:07:52,870 --> 00:07:54,800
He can go to Shanghai for you.

122
00:07:56,710 --> 00:07:57,790
Can't you feel it?

123
00:07:57,990 --> 00:07:59,290
Not even a bit?

124
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:01,280
I can only feel money now.

125
00:08:01,590 --> 00:08:03,030
And I'm seriously short on sleep.

126
00:08:03,030 --> 00:08:04,090
I want to take a nap.

127
00:08:19,150 --> 00:08:21,410
How did you know that we came to Shanghai?

128
00:08:21,590 --> 00:08:23,590
How could you not come when Wen Li is in Shanghai?

129
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:24,030
Besides,

130
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:25,960
I'll know once I check the flights.

131
00:08:26,560 --> 00:08:27,460
You feel so full of yourself.

132
00:08:27,460 --> 00:08:29,220
Is she that important to me?

133
00:08:29,370 --> 00:08:31,070
I don't know if she's that important to you,

134
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,730
but I'm very important to you.

135
00:08:33,590 --> 00:08:34,950
Who gave you the right to talk nonsense?

136
00:08:34,950 --> 00:08:36,210
Give me your suitcase.

137
00:08:36,870 --> 00:08:38,330
You have a car in Shanghai?

138
00:08:38,419 --> 00:08:39,390
It's rented.

139
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:46,930
Thank you.

140
00:09:06,350 --> 00:09:07,480
Look at you two.

141
00:09:08,250 --> 00:09:10,610
I told you to fly first class to watch me fight.

142
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:11,470
You wouldn't listen to me.

143
00:09:11,470 --> 00:09:13,900
You have to fly coach and exhaust yourselves.

144
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:14,740
Why bother?

145
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,870
Save money for me?

146
00:09:17,430 --> 00:09:18,350
No need.

147
00:09:18,350 --> 00:09:20,880
I make a ton of money. I'll reimburse you for the plane tickets.

148
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,280
How's it going over here?

149
00:09:23,990 --> 00:09:24,920
I told you.

150
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:25,990
We didn't need to bring this to court.

151
00:09:25,990 --> 00:09:27,230
Just two meetings.

152
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:28,170
Two meetings,

153
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,310
and I got her to transfer the 31 million yuan

154
00:09:30,310 --> 00:09:32,370
to Ms. Xiao's account.

155
00:09:32,400 --> 00:09:33,640
Am I awesome?

156
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:36,480
You found the account she used to transfer the money?

157
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,410
I looked into it.

158
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,630
It's just an account from a third party.

159
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:42,590
It has no connection to Wen Li,

160
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,950
and there is only one bank transaction.

161
00:09:44,950 --> 00:09:47,620
It must be an account that is used to transfer money.

162
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:48,880
Do you hear that, Qiu Hua?

163
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:49,760
How cunning.

164
00:09:49,990 --> 00:09:51,430
What is she doing now?

165
00:09:52,510 --> 00:09:55,510
On one hand, she has been encouraging Ding Qiwei

166
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:56,950
to take over the company's sales department.

167
00:09:56,950 --> 00:09:58,430
However, she didn't expect

168
00:09:58,430 --> 00:09:59,490
that his father would want

169
00:09:59,490 --> 00:10:02,090
to groom his son to take over the firm,

170
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,470
yet he wouldn't give it to his son so easily.

171
00:10:04,470 --> 00:10:05,310
On the other hand,

172
00:10:05,310 --> 00:10:06,770
she always wanted to sign the sales agency contract

173
00:10:06,770 --> 00:10:08,560
with Ding Qiwei's father.

174
00:10:08,710 --> 00:10:10,590
But his father won't budge.

175
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,830
So she's in a dilemma now.

176
00:10:13,370 --> 00:10:15,170
One step forward,

177
00:10:15,310 --> 00:10:17,890
and she doesn't know if she can take Ding Qiwei's father.

178
00:10:17,890 --> 00:10:18,910
If she takes a step back,

179
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,670
she doesn't want to make a losing deal.

180
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,830
After all, she has lost

181
00:10:21,830 --> 00:10:23,320
31 million yuan.

182
00:10:25,470 --> 00:10:26,590
Anyway,

183
00:10:26,590 --> 00:10:28,860
even if she can't take Ding Qiwei's father,

184
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:31,390
she has Ding Qiwei wrapped around her finger.

185
00:10:40,990 --> 00:10:43,160
This hotel is actually quite nice.

186
00:10:43,470 --> 00:10:45,870
Most importantly, Wen Li lives in the hotel across the street.

187
00:10:45,870 --> 00:10:47,510
You can see her in your room.

188
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,990
I've arranged everything in the room.

189
00:10:49,990 --> 00:10:50,750
I'll go upstairs with you later

190
00:10:50,750 --> 00:10:52,340
-and explain to you in detail.
-No need.

191
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,540
Thank you, Chen Shuo.

192
00:10:54,450 --> 00:10:56,510
We can handle it ourselves from here.

193
00:10:57,310 --> 00:10:58,670
Shall we take a break?

194
00:10:58,740 --> 00:10:59,370
Sure.

195
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:00,010
Okay.

196
00:11:01,950 --> 00:11:03,480
We'll contact you tomorrow

197
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:05,350
and discuss the next strategy.

198
00:11:07,470 --> 00:11:07,830
Fine.

199
00:11:07,830 --> 00:11:08,190
Okay.

200
00:13:44,920 --> 00:13:47,820
[Ding Qiwei]

201
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:57,820
Hello, Qiwei.

202
00:13:58,110 --> 00:13:58,560
Wen Li.

203
00:13:58,670 --> 00:13:59,940
I got a text from the bank.

204
00:13:59,940 --> 00:14:02,000
You transferred 2 million yuan to me?

205
00:14:03,990 --> 00:14:04,830
Yes.

206
00:14:05,090 --> 00:14:06,560
Didn't we agree

207
00:14:06,590 --> 00:14:07,880
that I gave you some startup funds?

208
00:14:07,880 --> 00:14:08,440
Wen Li!

209
00:14:08,760 --> 00:14:10,130
What should I say?

210
00:14:10,160 --> 00:14:11,710
I'm so lucky.

211
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,400
I finally met you

212
00:14:13,440 --> 00:14:14,970
during my pursuit of art.

213
00:14:15,610 --> 00:14:17,540
Where are you now? I want to see you.

214
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:19,540
Now?

215
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:24,570
It's getting late.

216
00:14:24,670 --> 00:14:25,830
Why don't we meet another time?

217
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:26,580
No.

218
00:14:27,220 --> 00:14:28,630
I'm so excited now.

219
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:30,290
I need to see you now.

220
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:33,580
I'm sorry.

221
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:36,470
I haven't been feeling well, both physically and emotionally, lately.

222
00:14:36,470 --> 00:14:38,400
I was feeling incredibly lonely in my apartment,

223
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:39,660
so I moved to a hotel.

224
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:41,870
Which hotel are you staying at?

225
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:43,530
Can you send me your location?

226
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,600
Okay.

227
00:14:48,820 --> 00:14:49,810
I'll send it to you now.

228
00:14:49,810 --> 00:14:51,680
Okay, I'll be right there.

229
00:15:36,050 --> 00:15:36,700
Wen Li.

230
00:15:36,980 --> 00:15:39,080
Is it too late...

231
00:15:39,110 --> 00:15:39,840
How about...

232
00:15:59,070 --> 00:15:59,800
He's coming.

233
00:16:00,230 --> 00:16:02,030
Beauties, how did you sleep?

234
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:06,880
Unscrupulous Chen.

235
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,350
Let's get down to business.

236
00:16:08,350 --> 00:16:09,550
Tell me what you know.

237
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:15,650
Okay, let me know if you have any news.

238
00:16:17,510 --> 00:16:19,180
I've been busy with your business all morning.

239
00:16:19,180 --> 00:16:20,690
You didn't even say something nice to me first.

240
00:16:20,690 --> 00:16:21,890
So straightforward.

241
00:16:24,070 --> 00:16:25,130
Am I right, Ms. Qiu?

242
00:16:28,130 --> 00:16:30,190
Aren't you tired of being so uptight?

243
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:31,050
No.

244
00:16:31,560 --> 00:16:32,690
I feel tired for you.

245
00:16:38,900 --> 00:16:39,980
Wen Li

246
00:16:40,170 --> 00:16:42,280
is speeding up her pace.

247
00:16:42,670 --> 00:16:44,180
I met someone last night.

248
00:16:44,430 --> 00:16:46,390
Wen Li spent 30,000 yuan on him.

249
00:16:46,830 --> 00:16:49,030
Wen Li could even spend money on others?

250
00:16:49,190 --> 00:16:50,860
She bought a movie script from him.

251
00:16:50,860 --> 00:16:52,300
You should know

252
00:16:52,330 --> 00:16:54,060
who currently has the script, right?

253
00:16:54,060 --> 00:16:55,860
Ding Qiwei. Who else could it be?

254
00:16:58,240 --> 00:16:58,960
Wen Li...

255
00:16:58,990 --> 00:17:01,290
has turned herself into a screenwriter.

256
00:17:02,570 --> 00:17:03,410
For money,

257
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:06,440
she really goes to great lengths.

258
00:17:06,710 --> 00:17:07,270
Mr. Chen,

259
00:17:07,450 --> 00:17:08,190
didn't you say that Ding Qiwei

260
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:10,450
is the head of Boshi's sales department?

261
00:17:10,599 --> 00:17:11,310
Then why did Wen Li

262
00:17:11,310 --> 00:17:13,109
still play these little tricks?

263
00:17:15,160 --> 00:17:16,890
Qiwei is just a rich kid.

264
00:17:17,109 --> 00:17:18,829
Ding Zhaoguang knows his son well.

265
00:17:18,829 --> 00:17:20,910
So Qiwei

266
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:22,790
is the sales director, nominally.

267
00:17:22,790 --> 00:17:24,750
Looks like, Wen Li knows that as well.

268
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:26,140
She's trying another way.

269
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:26,869
Definitely.

270
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:29,840
Yingzi and I think

271
00:17:29,840 --> 00:17:31,710
that we should meet Ding Zhaoguang.

272
00:17:31,710 --> 00:17:33,040
Let's be more discreet.

273
00:17:33,390 --> 00:17:35,110
My informant told me

274
00:17:35,140 --> 00:17:37,230
that Ding Qiwei went to his father today

275
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:39,180
and asked him to transfer himself to Jingbei,

276
00:17:39,180 --> 00:17:41,240
in charge of the branch office there.

277
00:17:42,570 --> 00:17:43,850
Good job, Mr. Chen.

278
00:17:44,010 --> 00:17:44,510
No.

279
00:17:44,800 --> 00:17:45,930
Unscrupulous Chen.

280
00:17:47,390 --> 00:17:49,620
You've even planted a mole around him.

281
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:51,470
Didn't I tell you

282
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:53,760
that no one can escape me?

283
00:17:53,790 --> 00:17:55,590
Stop there. That one is too much.

284
00:17:57,190 --> 00:17:59,630
