390
00:22:36,630 --> 00:22:37,240
Mr. Ding.

391
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:38,420
Come in.

392
00:22:42,190 --> 00:22:42,530
Please.

393
00:22:42,530 --> 00:22:43,130
Thank you.

394
00:22:43,670 --> 00:22:45,760
