396
00:22:46,490 --> 00:22:47,690
Let me introduce you.

397
00:22:47,910 --> 00:22:49,110
This is Mrs. Luo.

398
00:22:49,130 --> 00:22:50,030
Hello, Mr. Ding.

399
00:22:50,030 --> 00:22:50,430
Hello.

400
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:51,060
This is Ms. Qiu.

401
00:22:51,060 --> 00:22:51,540
Hello.

402
00:22:51,560 --> 00:22:51,960
Hello.

403
00:22:53,110 --> 00:22:54,990
We're here today

404
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:57,710
