405
00:22:58,220 --> 00:22:58,900
Wen Li?

406
00:23:00,150 --> 00:23:02,230
That woman who has been coming to my company frequently?

407
00:23:02,230 --> 00:23:02,830
Yes.

408
00:23:03,630 --> 00:23:04,870
What's going on between her and my son?

409
00:23:04,870 --> 00:23:06,350
As we speak, your son

410
00:23:06,370 --> 00:23:08,970
