411
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:22,630
Here.

412
00:23:27,730 --> 00:23:28,460
Uncle Liang!

413
00:23:31,630 --> 00:23:32,360
Uncle Liang.

414
00:23:32,820 --> 00:23:33,810
Qiwei.

