419
00:23:40,520 --> 00:23:41,710
Let me introduce you, Uncle Liang.

420
00:23:41,710 --> 00:23:42,510
This is Wen Li.

421
00:23:42,510 --> 00:23:43,630
He's my business partner.

422
00:23:43,260 --> 00:23:47,570
[General Manager of Boshi Group Jingbei Branch, Liang Weidong]

423
00:23:43,770 --> 00:23:44,700
Nice to meet you.

424
00:23:44,890 --> 00:23:45,560
Partner?

425
00:23:46,110 --> 00:23:47,630
