426
00:23:47,630 --> 00:23:48,360
Uncle Liang.

427
00:23:48,460 --> 00:23:50,170
She's my partner in making movies.

428
00:23:50,170 --> 00:23:50,840
She is a scriptwriter.

429
00:23:50,840 --> 00:23:51,840
I'm the director.

430
00:23:53,630 --> 00:23:55,990
Uncle Liang, I'm looking forward to working with you.

431
00:23:55,990 --> 00:23:57,270
You said that Sun Huading

432
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:58,810
