464
00:25:05,650 --> 00:25:06,430
Hello, Mr. Liang.

465
00:25:06,430 --> 00:25:08,890
This area was designed by Mr. Liang himself.

466
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:10,610
You have good taste, Uncle Liang.

467
00:25:10,610 --> 00:25:11,500
I'm old.

468
00:25:11,920 --> 00:25:12,990
-Let's go.
-Hello, Mr. Liang.

469
00:25:12,990 --> 00:25:14,750
