476
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:38,190
Make a movie.

477
00:25:45,610 --> 00:25:47,580
No wonder he went to Jingbei.

478
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,080
How is it?

479
00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:51,130
It's good, Uncle Liang.

480
00:25:52,050 --> 00:25:53,480
Uncle Liang. Don't worry.

481
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:55,140
I'll take care of the company.

482
00:25:56,030 --> 00:25:57,990
Children will grow up eventually.

