486
00:26:07,360 --> 00:26:08,330
No, Uncle Liang.

487
00:26:08,430 --> 00:26:10,250
Wen Li will be our partner from now on.

488
00:26:10,250 --> 00:26:11,950
We don't have to hide anything from her.

489
00:26:11,950 --> 00:26:12,950
It's better for us

490
00:26:13,270 --> 00:26:15,870
to discuss the company's business privately.

491
00:26:16,550 --> 00:26:17,230
Miss Wen.

492
00:26:18,570 --> 00:26:20,430
Qiwei, I'll wait for you outside.

493
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:25,260
They are in Jingbei now.

494
00:26:26,210 --> 00:26:26,960
