517
00:27:20,370 --> 00:27:21,460
Qiwei is here.

518
00:27:21,950 --> 00:27:23,240
Let's talk privately.

519
00:27:32,690 --> 00:27:33,330
Uncle.

520
00:27:33,790 --> 00:27:35,430
You've been on the phone with my dad for so long.

521
00:27:35,430 --> 00:27:36,560
Is everything okay?

522
00:27:37,150 --> 00:27:38,410
Come, sit down, Qiwei.

523
00:27:41,230 --> 00:27:42,070
Nothing.

524
00:27:42,440 --> 00:27:43,570
Your dad has asked me

525
00:27:43,620 --> 00:27:46,700
