531
00:27:58,310 --> 00:28:00,110
and to take care of it for a while.

532
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:01,800
CFO?

533
00:28:05,700 --> 00:28:06,370
Qiwei.

534
00:28:06,500 --> 00:28:08,610
