536
00:28:10,550 --> 00:28:11,110
Well...

537
00:28:11,540 --> 00:28:12,670
It's nothing.

538
00:28:12,690 --> 00:28:14,660
We're not here for money, anyway.

539
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:15,920
Besides,

540
00:28:15,950 --> 00:28:17,450
with Uncle Liang here to take care of the company,

541
00:28:17,450 --> 00:28:19,250
we will have time to film a movie.

542
00:28:19,950 --> 00:28:20,990
I've agreed.

543
00:28:25,090 --> 00:28:26,020
What do you mean?

544
00:28:26,930 --> 00:28:28,370
Give her some money?

545
00:28:29,970 --> 00:28:30,850
Why?

546
00:28:31,540 --> 00:28:33,340
To get evidence of her crime.

547
00:28:34,750 --> 00:28:35,990
Based on what we know about her,

548
00:28:35,990 --> 00:28:37,650
