554
00:28:45,700 --> 00:28:47,080
the accounts of her own company yet.

555
00:28:47,080 --> 00:28:49,160
We need to locate this hidden account

556
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:51,440
and trace her entire transfer chain

557
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:53,240
in order to report her for fraud.

558
00:28:55,910 --> 00:28:58,030
