559
00:28:58,030 --> 00:29:00,030
once she has transferred it abroad?

560
00:29:00,390 --> 00:29:01,480
So, no.

561
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:02,910
I earned every penny

562
00:29:02,930 --> 00:29:04,660
through my hard work.

563
00:29:05,310 --> 00:29:07,340
I can't waste it on her.

564
00:29:08,180 --> 00:29:08,740
That's right.

565
00:29:08,740 --> 00:29:09,220
Right?

566
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:09,730
Yes.

567
00:29:10,710 --> 00:29:11,240
Mr. Ding.

568
00:29:11,360 --> 00:29:12,710
Actually, we understand

569
00:29:12,710 --> 00:29:14,270
that you value your wealth.

570
00:29:14,720 --> 00:29:15,800
With your wealth,

571
00:29:15,890 --> 00:29:17,460
you have such a big firm

572
00:29:17,520 --> 00:29:18,650
with a lot of employees.

573
00:29:18,650 --> 00:29:19,450
I understand.

574
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:20,420
But this is

575
00:29:20,420 --> 00:29:23,430
about your son, after all.

576
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:24,470
As far as we know,

577
00:29:24,470 --> 00:29:26,430
you are usually very strict with him.

578
00:29:26,430 --> 00:29:28,090
Why are you so strict with him?

579
00:29:28,670 --> 00:29:29,790
You want him to make it

580
00:29:29,790 --> 00:29:31,580
and take over your business.

581
00:29:31,830 --> 00:29:33,380
But Wen Li

582
00:29:34,020 --> 00:29:35,750
is frantically plotting ways.

583
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:37,880
When they are together,

584
00:29:38,720 --> 00:29:40,840
Qiwei may get hurt.

585
00:29:41,560 --> 00:29:43,200
But it's okay, young man.

586
00:29:43,270 --> 00:29:45,010
He'll grow up after this.

587
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:45,780
Right?

588
00:29:45,800 --> 00:29:48,400
If he gets hurt, bad things will turn into good.

589
00:29:48,890 --> 00:29:50,220
Maybe he will come back.

590
00:29:50,360 --> 00:29:52,280
You get what you want, right?

591
00:29:52,830 --> 00:29:53,580
Am I right?

592
00:29:57,480 --> 00:29:58,520
Just say it.

593
00:30:00,320 --> 00:30:01,520
What's your plan?

594
00:30:01,550 --> 00:30:02,230
30 million.

595
00:30:03,260 --> 00:30:04,520
Lend us 30 million yuan

596
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:05,500
to put on a show.

597
00:30:05,630 --> 00:30:07,110
Just for show.

598
00:30:07,210 --> 00:30:08,100
Let Wen Li think

599
00:30:08,120 --> 00:30:10,000
she has 30 million yuan to transfer.

600
00:30:10,000 --> 00:30:10,980
She's an idiot?

601
00:30:12,600 --> 00:30:14,890
There is a sum of money, but she can't touch it.

602
00:30:14,890 --> 00:30:16,150
Will she fall for this?

603
00:30:16,470 --> 00:30:17,270
You're right.

604
00:30:17,790 --> 00:30:19,180
So, we'll consider

605
00:30:19,510 --> 00:30:21,970
giving Wen Li a chance to transfer the money.

606
00:30:22,180 --> 00:30:24,640
And this time, we only need two million yuan.

607
00:30:29,750 --> 00:30:30,840
That means

608
00:30:31,700 --> 00:30:33,310
we'll use 30 million yuan as bait to keep her on the hook

609
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:37,370
and two million yuan to make her believe she can get her hands on the money.

610
00:30:37,870 --> 00:30:40,370
Can you gather the evidence during this period?

611
00:30:40,370 --> 00:30:42,140
We will do our best.

612
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:43,910
As long as we find

613
00:30:43,910 --> 00:30:45,170
this hidden account,

614
00:30:45,200 --> 00:30:46,930
we can report her to the police.

615
00:30:51,350 --> 00:30:52,040
Fine.

616
00:30:53,280 --> 00:30:55,070
I'll only give you two million yuan.

617
00:30:55,070 --> 00:30:56,600
Whether it succeeds or not,

618
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:58,280
I won't pay any more.

619
00:30:58,320 --> 00:30:59,750
Okay, thank you.

620
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:01,400
I think

621
00:31:01,660 --> 00:31:03,060
Wen Li should actually go after Ding Zhaoguang

622
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:04,700
instead of his son.

623
00:31:05,070 --> 00:31:06,990
They are a perfect match.

624
00:31:21,470 --> 00:31:22,190
Hold on.

625
00:31:23,010 --> 00:31:23,620
What?

626
00:31:28,060 --> 00:31:29,390
Okay, this way, please.

627
00:31:49,030 --> 00:31:51,120
What's wrong with those security guards?

628
00:31:51,120 --> 00:31:52,430
Why do they have to report to someone

629
00:31:52,430 --> 00:31:53,910
when I come to the company?

630
00:31:58,500 --> 00:31:59,230
Don't panic.

631
00:32:00,830 --> 00:32:01,760
You can't panic.

632
00:32:02,410 --> 00:32:05,070
If you panic, all of your efforts will be in vain.

633
00:32:06,570 --> 00:32:08,300
What's wrong with Uncle Liang?

634
00:32:09,080 --> 00:32:10,230
He's the CFO,

635
00:32:10,230 --> 00:32:11,670
so I can't get a penny.

636
00:32:13,020 --> 00:32:14,550
Did they notice something?

637
00:32:15,040 --> 00:32:17,300
Or has that 30 million yuan been exposed?

638
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:20,550
Maybe I should go.

639
00:32:20,850 --> 00:32:23,180
It'd be troublesome if they already knew.

640
00:32:37,320 --> 00:32:38,070
But

641
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:40,810
he is almost about to take the bait.

642
00:32:44,350 --> 00:32:45,200
Go for it.

643
00:32:45,870 --> 00:32:47,630
If he can still get his hands on the money,

644
00:32:47,630 --> 00:32:48,690
it means it's fine.

645
00:32:49,140 --> 00:32:50,700
If he can't...

646
00:32:53,080 --> 00:32:54,360
Wen Li, I'm sorry.

647
00:32:54,610 --> 00:32:56,670
I know the two million yuan are yours.

648
00:32:56,790 --> 00:32:58,470
If you have any other ideas...

649
00:32:58,740 --> 00:32:59,580
Qiwei.

650
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:00,910
Aren't we determined

651
00:33:00,910 --> 00:33:02,520
to make a great film?

652
00:33:03,230 --> 00:33:04,920
If we make it in a hurry,

653
00:33:04,950 --> 00:33:06,340
what's the point?

654
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,880
That's true.

655
00:33:10,230 --> 00:33:12,960
But my dad doesn't support me making movies at all.

656
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:14,760
He won't give us any money.

657
00:33:18,870 --> 00:33:19,510
Qiwei.

658
00:33:20,310 --> 00:33:21,440
Let's go to America.

659
00:33:22,100 --> 00:33:24,030
Go to Hollywood for further study.

660
00:33:24,500 --> 00:33:26,450
When we become more mature in art,

661
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:28,280
we can make the movies we want

662
00:33:28,360 --> 00:33:29,100
at that time.

663
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:30,150
But

664
00:33:30,190 --> 00:33:31,830
I don't think there are many opportunities

665
00:33:31,830 --> 00:33:33,690
for Chinese people in Hollywood.

666
00:33:34,150 --> 00:33:35,630
How come?

667
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:38,070
Director Ang Lee is also Chinese.

668
00:33:39,270 --> 00:33:40,270
If we want to do it,

669
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:43,950
we must become the world's best director and scriptwriter.

670
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:46,680
But I'm afraid

671
00:33:46,710 --> 00:33:47,990
that if I want to reach the level of Ang Lee...

672
00:33:47,990 --> 00:33:49,310
In my eyes,

673
00:33:49,900 --> 00:33:51,180
you're Ang Lee.

674
00:33:54,870 --> 00:33:57,270
You're going to America to open a business?

675
00:33:57,780 --> 00:33:58,870
Qiwei.

676
00:33:59,110 --> 00:34:01,830
You're not familiar with the business here yet.

677
00:34:01,850 --> 00:34:02,350
You...

678
00:34:02,370 --> 00:34:04,380
Uncle Liang, which side are you on?

679
00:34:04,830 --> 00:34:06,070
If you side with my dad,

680
00:34:06,070 --> 00:34:07,310
I'm quitting now.

681
00:34:07,410 --> 00:34:09,250
And I will go to America right away with Wen Li.

682
00:34:09,250 --> 00:34:09,980
Okay.

683
00:34:10,310 --> 00:34:11,510
Let me think about it.

684
00:34:11,650 --> 00:34:13,750
Let me think about how to report to your dad.

685
00:34:13,750 --> 00:34:15,010
Hurry up, Uncle Liang.

686
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:17,050
I'll go back and wait for your news.

687
00:34:45,929 --> 00:34:46,370
Hello.

688
00:34:51,110 --> 00:34:52,639
They really took this step.

689
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:56,510
Fine.

690
00:34:59,030 --> 00:35:00,560
You answer him like this...

691
00:35:02,520 --> 00:35:03,470
Have my cameras arrived yet?

692
00:35:03,470 --> 00:35:04,990
No, Mr. Ding.

693
00:35:05,200 --> 00:35:06,320
Tell me when they arrive.

694
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,400
Okay, Mr. Ding.

695
00:35:08,270 --> 00:35:08,870
Wen Li.

696
00:35:12,010 --> 00:35:12,600
Qiwei!

697
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:16,410
No one asked about who I was when I came to the company.

698
00:35:16,410 --> 00:35:19,270
Why did the security guards have to call someone during these times?

699
00:35:19,270 --> 00:35:20,270
Did they call you?

700
00:35:20,720 --> 00:35:21,920
No.

701
00:35:22,560 --> 00:35:24,400
I guess they called Uncle Liang.

702
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:25,520
It doesn't matter.

703
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:26,890
Wen Li, I have good news.

704
00:35:27,470 --> 00:35:28,390
My dad has agreed

705
00:35:28,390 --> 00:35:29,920
to send us money to America.

706
00:35:30,590 --> 00:35:31,510
That's great.

707
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:34,110
And my dad said he would give us 30 million yuan.

708
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,560
But he transferred the 30 million yuan

709
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:38,290
to Uncle Liang for now.

710
00:35:38,310 --> 00:35:40,340
Uncle Liang only transferred 2 million yuan to me.

711
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:41,280
But Uncle Liang said

712
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:43,810
that he could transfer the rest to us anytime.

713
00:35:44,120 --> 00:35:45,510
That's great.

714
00:35:46,900 --> 00:35:47,780
Qiwei,

715
00:35:48,000 --> 00:35:49,920
your dad still cares about you.

716
00:35:50,330 --> 00:35:52,620
He asked Uncle Liang to give us so much money.

717
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:53,830
He doesn't want you to have a hard time dealing with something

718
00:35:53,830 --> 00:35:55,090
when you go to America.

719
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:57,880
I talked to them

720
00:35:57,910 --> 00:35:59,710
very seriously this time, okay?

721
00:35:59,910 --> 00:36:00,600
I think

722
00:36:00,630 --> 00:36:03,030
I should be tougher with them in the future.

723
00:36:05,190 --> 00:36:06,110
Yes.

724
00:36:06,700 --> 00:36:08,460
We have to stick to our dreams.

725
00:36:08,930 --> 00:36:11,400
You can do it! I trust you!

726
00:36:13,750 --> 00:36:14,910
Wen Li

727
00:36:15,320 --> 00:36:17,710
gave us an account in her name.

728
00:36:18,270 --> 00:36:19,470
Is this that account?

729
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:23,020
Wen Li is too cunning.

730
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:27,920
[Company Account, Business to Business]

731
00:36:24,600 --> 00:36:27,920
[Jingbei Ming Xin Information Technology Co.]

732
00:36:25,110 --> 00:36:27,840
She transferred Ming Xin's money a long time ago.

733
00:36:27,960 --> 00:36:29,990
I thought she wouldn't use this account anymore.

734
00:36:29,990 --> 00:36:31,920
I didn't expect her to use it again.

735
00:36:32,910 --> 00:36:33,630
No.

736
00:36:34,020 --> 00:36:36,050
I can't let her use this account anymore.

737
00:36:36,050 --> 00:36:38,450
We might need your help later, Uncle Liang.

738
00:36:38,930 --> 00:36:41,070
Does she agree to transfer only 2 million yuan to her this time?

739
00:36:41,070 --> 00:36:42,600
She wouldn't dare to say no.

740
00:36:42,700 --> 00:36:44,350
She's still after our Qiwei.

741
00:36:45,020 --> 00:36:47,070
If she acted too eagerly,

742
00:36:47,510 --> 00:36:48,990
she would scare Qiwei.

743
00:36:50,190 --> 00:36:51,630
Our Qiwei

744
00:36:51,950 --> 00:36:53,120
is such a silly kid.

745
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:56,910
Do you know

746
00:36:56,910 --> 00:36:58,310
what they are going to do?

747
00:36:58,390 --> 00:37:00,720
Kaiwei is busy filming a movie in America.

748
00:37:02,830 --> 00:37:05,580
Wen Li seems a bit hesitant.

749
00:37:05,910 --> 00:37:06,610
I think

750
00:37:07,120 --> 00:37:09,220
that she's supposed to be waiting for the money

751
00:37:09,220 --> 00:37:11,000
to be deposited into her account.

752
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:12,910
This woman is really greedy.

753
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:14,800
It's okay.

754
00:37:15,030 --> 00:37:17,030
We'll follow the plan later.

755
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:20,160
Is there anything else I can do?

756
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:21,930
Let's keep in touch.

757
00:37:22,550 --> 00:37:23,220
Okay.

758
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,420
-I gotta go.
-Okay.

759
00:37:28,240 --> 00:37:29,840
Qiwei has been busy

760
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:31,280
booking tickets.

761
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:34,560
Wen Li hasn't shown up at our company for days.

762
00:37:34,820 --> 00:37:37,130
Could she have run away?

763
00:37:37,520 --> 00:37:38,350
Don't worry.

764
00:37:38,750 --> 00:37:40,960
Wen Li won't let Qiwei off easily.

765
00:37:40,980 --> 00:37:43,640
You just have to keep an eye on Young Master Ding.

766
00:37:43,900 --> 00:37:44,540
Okay.

767
00:37:45,250 --> 00:37:46,040
I'll leave now.

768
00:37:46,040 --> 00:37:47,040
Let me see you off.

769
00:37:53,040 --> 00:37:55,200
Now it's Liu Ming's parents' turn.

770
00:37:58,180 --> 00:37:58,870
Coming.

771
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:04,200
Uncle, Auntie.

772
00:38:04,830 --> 00:38:06,530
Xia, how could you let her in?

773
00:38:06,710 --> 00:38:08,040
What are you doing here?

774
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:09,590
I really don't want to be here.

775
00:38:09,590 --> 00:38:10,160
But I think

776
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:12,020
I have to remind you of something.

777
00:38:12,430 --> 00:38:14,030
You, Liu Ming, and Wen Li

778
00:38:14,120 --> 00:38:16,980
have registered a company called Ming Xin Company.

779
00:38:17,270 --> 00:38:18,600
Your company's account

780
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:20,420
has been emptied.

781
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:21,190
What?

782
00:38:21,190 --> 00:38:21,750
What did you say?

783
00:38:21,750 --> 00:38:22,270
What?

784
00:38:23,940 --> 00:38:24,730
Emptied?

785
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:26,690
What do you mean by that?

786
00:38:27,220 --> 00:38:27,880
Take a look.

787
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:29,920
Do you know the person in this photo

788
00:38:30,230 --> 00:38:31,490
and where the place is?

789
00:38:33,070 --> 00:38:33,870
Isn't this...

790
00:38:34,980 --> 00:38:35,760
Wen Li?

791
00:38:36,640 --> 00:38:37,320
Shanghai.

792
00:38:37,700 --> 00:38:38,540
Impossible.

793
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:40,550
The daughter-in-law you had in mind

794
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:41,630
has returned to China.

795
00:38:41,630 --> 00:38:43,360
How can your precious son, Liu Ming,

796
00:38:43,360 --> 00:38:44,590
manage to have a baby

797
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:46,040
on his own in the US?

798
00:38:47,240 --> 00:38:48,150
No way.

799
00:38:48,310 --> 00:38:50,790
Liu Ming and she are both in the US now.

800
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:51,380
Yes.

801
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:53,120
They played tricks on me

802
00:38:53,310 --> 00:38:55,790
and transferred all of my money to the account of that company.

803
00:38:55,790 --> 00:38:56,720
Go check

804
00:38:56,750 --> 00:38:58,290
that company's account for yourself.

805
00:38:58,290 --> 00:39:00,320
If you don't trust me, check

806
00:39:00,350 --> 00:39:02,410
if there's any money in your account.

807
00:39:03,630 --> 00:39:05,320
See where the money has been transferred to.

808
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,670
I can do the rest.

809
00:39:07,420 --> 00:39:09,130
You know where to find me.

810
00:39:11,550 --> 00:39:12,550
Why did Wen Li come back?

811
00:39:12,550 --> 00:39:13,350
Hurry up!

812
00:39:13,380 --> 00:39:14,770
What happened to the money?

813
00:39:14,770 --> 00:39:15,700
Check the account.

814
00:39:15,700 --> 00:39:16,830
Using the computer.

815
00:39:16,830 --> 00:39:17,340
Yes.

816
00:39:18,190 --> 00:39:19,720
Xia, power on the computer.

817
00:39:25,370 --> 00:39:26,860
We are humans.

818
00:39:27,390 --> 00:39:32,260
We should learn to be compassionate towards the suffering in the world.

819
00:39:32,910 --> 00:39:33,830
Forget it, Dad.

820
00:39:33,990 --> 00:39:36,990
You're back to your old ways, returning good for evil.

821
00:39:38,310 --> 00:39:39,070
I think

822
00:39:39,140 --> 00:39:40,890
Chen Shuo is right about this.

823
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:42,930
Indulging bad people

824
00:39:42,930 --> 00:39:45,130
is the greatest cruelty to good people.

825
00:39:48,350 --> 00:39:49,030
Yingzi.

826
00:39:49,700 --> 00:39:52,830
You have always mentioned Chen Shuo since you came back.

827
00:39:53,210 --> 00:39:54,250
What does he do?

828
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:58,030
Do I always mention him?

829
00:39:58,030 --> 00:39:59,490
You always mentioned him.

830
00:40:00,910 --> 00:40:02,190
Chen Shuo is...

831
00:40:02,470 --> 00:40:04,950
Maybe he's helping me with Wen Li's case.

832
00:40:06,050 --> 00:40:07,360
He's a lawyer

833
00:40:07,660 --> 00:40:08,920
from another law firm.

834
00:40:10,630 --> 00:40:12,040
I think

835
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:13,760
you like him.

836
00:40:16,460 --> 00:40:16,990
Dad.

837
00:40:17,470 --> 00:40:18,390
No.

838
00:40:18,590 --> 00:40:20,040
How could I like him?

839
00:40:20,470 --> 00:40:21,390
You like him.

840
00:40:21,460 --> 00:40:22,670
I can feel it.

841
00:40:25,080 --> 00:40:25,790
Yingzi.

842
00:40:25,890 --> 00:40:27,360
Your relationship with Liu Ming

843
00:40:27,360 --> 00:40:28,970
no longer exists.

844
00:40:29,590 --> 00:40:31,060
As soon as the trial starts,

845
00:40:31,060 --> 00:40:32,580
you two are no longer

846
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,440
married to each other.

847
00:40:34,780 --> 00:40:37,420
You should consider moving on.

848
00:40:38,630 --> 00:40:41,510
I'm not going to think about being in a relationship for now.

849
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:44,370
I'm going to think about getting married even more.

850
00:40:45,630 --> 00:40:47,390
You should have faith

851
00:40:47,470 --> 00:40:50,060
in love and family.

852
00:40:50,250 --> 00:40:51,420
Should I?

853
00:40:52,900 --> 00:40:54,700
Dad, to be honest,

854
00:40:55,670 --> 00:40:56,800
I'm already scared.

855
00:40:59,550 --> 00:41:01,110
You have to.

856
00:41:01,380 --> 00:41:01,980
Look.

857
00:41:02,390 --> 00:41:04,640
Your mother, I, and you.

858
00:41:04,670 --> 00:41:05,590
The three of us

859
00:41:05,890 --> 00:41:08,040
have been living happily

860
00:41:08,050 --> 00:41:09,050
for so many years.

861
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:10,890
Isn't this the best relationship

862
00:41:10,890 --> 00:41:12,590
in the world?

863
00:41:13,830 --> 00:41:14,390
Dad,

864
00:41:15,990 --> 00:41:18,190
I'm really lucky

865
00:41:18,760 --> 00:41:20,580
to have grown up in such a loving family.

866
00:41:20,580 --> 00:41:22,690
That's because I have a father like you.

867
00:41:22,690 --> 00:41:25,110
You believe that people are kind.

868
00:41:27,190 --> 00:41:29,390
But after going through so many things,

869
00:41:29,950 --> 00:41:31,410
I can no longer be like you.

870
00:41:32,370 --> 00:41:32,960
But

871
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:36,150
we still need to have a family.

872
00:41:37,370 --> 00:41:39,200
How many scammers

873
00:41:39,910 --> 00:41:41,110
like Liu Ming are there in the world?

874
00:41:41,110 --> 00:41:41,630
Dad.

875
00:41:42,030 --> 00:41:43,690
It doesn't matter that I have my own family.

876
00:41:43,690 --> 00:41:45,670
I have you and my mom, and that is enough.

877
00:41:45,670 --> 00:41:47,530
Marriage is even less important.

878
00:41:48,860 --> 00:41:50,030
My ultimate goal

879
00:41:50,330 --> 00:41:52,470
is to learn how to take control of my own life,

880
00:41:52,470 --> 00:41:53,670
right?

881
00:41:54,640 --> 00:41:55,440
By then,

882
00:41:56,270 --> 00:41:57,690
even if I meet someone like Liu Ming again,

883
00:41:57,690 --> 00:41:58,750
I'll not be afraid.

884
00:42:14,220 --> 00:42:15,390
Hello, Qiwei.

885
00:42:15,790 --> 00:42:17,390
Wen Li, when are we going to the US?

886
00:42:17,390 --> 00:42:18,760
My visa is ready.

887
00:42:18,780 --> 00:42:20,240
I've checked the flights.

888
00:42:22,500 --> 00:42:23,510
What's the hurry?

889
00:42:24,010 --> 00:42:25,880
We have too little money.

890
00:42:26,070 --> 00:42:28,330
We won't have enough money for the movie.

891
00:42:28,530 --> 00:42:30,730
Have you mentioned this to Uncle Liang?

892
00:42:30,990 --> 00:42:31,830
Yes.

893
00:42:32,000 --> 00:42:33,010
But Uncle Liang said

894
00:42:33,010 --> 00:42:33,590
that we have to wait

895
00:42:33,590 --> 00:42:35,270
until we really need money,

896
00:42:35,270 --> 00:42:36,330
and then he will give it to us.

897
00:42:36,330 --> 00:42:37,830
We haven't done anything yet.

898
00:42:37,830 --> 00:42:39,470
He can't give us more money.

899
00:42:40,300 --> 00:42:42,580
You can't do business like this.

900
00:42:42,970 --> 00:42:44,320
If we were in urgent need of money,

901
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,680
wouldn't things get delayed?

902
00:42:45,680 --> 00:42:47,420
Are your dad and Uncle Liang playing you?

903
00:42:47,420 --> 00:42:49,580
Why would they do that to me?

904
00:42:52,340 --> 00:42:53,900
Okay, there's no need to rush.

905
00:42:53,900 --> 00:42:55,220
We'll talk about it till the money comes in.
